blog.name: i-cant-handle-the-cravings
blog.title: a sad little emo with an eating disorder;
blog.description:
girl - call me Em - eating disorder - depression - anxiety- i don’t support eds I support recovery- follow me for my ed journey, some tips, reminders, recipes, quotes and memes ❤️my goal is to maintain my weight❤️ DM me always looking for Ana buddies ❤️

maintain my weight ❤️

body:
hey

hey there, thanks for reading, you’ve stumbled onto my account.

a little bit about me:

I’m a girl

I have an eating disorder, depression, anxiety and OCD.

I love music, quotes and animals :)

I’m not really sure what this account is going to be like, but I’m hoping to post some tips and reminders for anyone recovering from an eating disorder, and some stuff about depression and self esteem too. Also some memes about eating disorders.

I don’t support any kind of eating disorder or mental illness and if you’re new here my best advice to you would be to get away from the world of eating disorders and talk to a doctor or family right away.

Unfortunatly some of us are in too deep in this eating disorder world and some of us just need some support along our journeys :)

I hope whoever is reading this has a great day, or if you’re having a crap day or night i hope it gets better. Remember that you matter and you’re amazing. Stay safe xx

body:
This time of year can be difficult for some. Did you know that if you text 686868 when you are feeling depressed or suicidal, a crisis worker will text you back immediately and will continue to text with you? Many people don’t like talking over the phone and would feel more comfortable texting.

This is a free service for anyone In Canada.

I know I would much rather text than talk. Happy holidays, everyone, and stay safe!
